  <section>
    <title>如何下载和安装词典<indexterm class="singular">
        <primary>词典</primary> <secondary>下载和安装</secondary>
      </indexterm></title>

    <para>Dictionaries in <application>OmegaT</application> are based on the
    StarDict or on the Lingvo DSL format. To install the necessary files for the StarDict format, proceed as follows:</para>

    <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
        <para>搜索所需的语言组合-例如在 <ulink url="https://sourceforge.net/p/omegat/wiki/Reference%20Material/ "><indexterm class="singular">
            <primary>词典</primary> <secondary>StarDict</secondary>
          </indexterm>由OmegaT Wiki所给的词典链接</ulink></para>
      </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>

    <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
        <para>下载文件——其须为<filename>tarball</filename> 存档（扩展名为 <emphasis>tar.bz</emphasis> 或 <emphasis>tar.bz2</emphasis></para>
      </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>

    <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
        <para>Use untar utility (or its equivalent, for instance<filename>
        winrar</filename> in Windows) to extract its contents into the project
        folder &quot;Dictionary&quot;. There should be three files, with extensions
        <emphasis>dz, idx </emphasis>and <emphasis>ifo</emphasis>.</para>
      </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>

    <para>注意除了可以使用“原文-译文”类型的词典之外，通过词典功能还可以访问下列资源：</para>

    <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
        <para><indexterm class="singular">
            <primary>词典</primary> <secondary>韦氏词典</secondary>
          </indexterm>韦氏修订版同义词词典（1913）</para>
      </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>

    <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
        <para><indexterm class="singular">
            <primary>词典</primary> <secondary>朗文</secondary>
          </indexterm>朗文当代英语词典</para>
      </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>

    <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
        <para><indexterm class="singular">
            <primary>词典</primary> <secondary>不列颠</secondary>
          </indexterm>不列颠简明百科全书</para>
      </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>

    <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
        <para>...等等</para>
      </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>

    <para>Some of the dictionaries have no strings attached - i.e. are &quot;Free
    to use&quot;, and others, like the selection above, are under the GPL license.
    The following example shows Merriam Webster 10th dictionary &quot;in
    action&quot;:</para>

    <figure id="Dict.Merriam.Webster">
      <title><indexterm class="singular">
          <primary>词典</primary> <secondary>韦氏词典</secondary> <seealso>词典</seealso>
        </indexterm>Merriam Webster 词典——实际使用</title>

      <mediaobject>
        <imageobject role="html">
